data.description: Welcome to Hillsdale. This exceptional 4-sided brick home with 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. This quaint home offers an Eat in kitchen, full basement, and a nice-sized backyard. Appliances stay with the home. Perfect for anyone looking for that ideal fixer-upper, starter home, investor project, Investor flip for Section 8 (new rates), or wants to purchase early before the city builds new homes in the area and the home values increase. Home is being sold in its current condition (AS-IS). The neighborhood is under reconstruction and getting ready for more homes. Located close to the city, MetroLink, bus stop, and I-70. Could make a great rental property.
